* obeys prac-de-1
* . ^constraint[5].source = Canonical(ISiKPersonImGesundheitsberuf)
* identifier 1.. MS
  * ^slicing.discriminator.type = #pattern
  * ^slicing.discriminator.path = "$this"
  * ^slicing.rules = #open
